Perrito Tech is an original OpenFamiliar character.

The 4x4 pixel-art spritesheet was redesigned in July 2026 with an AI-assisted
workflow using photographs supplied by the operator as visual references for
their dark-brindle dog. No source photograph is embedded or distributed in the
pack. The generated art was chroma-keyed, normalized with nearest-neighbor
processing, and mapped only to symmetric, event-driven frames. Deterministic
palette variants modify small state-prop accent colors only. The character is
collar-free in every variant.

It does not intentionally reproduce a third-party character, logo, or brand.

